{"tid":1256856,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《蘋果》：美國會議員重推《人權與民主法案》　新版本限港明年實現普選","createTime":"2019-06-25T08:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T08:51:34.000Z","uid":160760,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8beecd29311d29f4da635716ef192b1a417acf","tid":1256856,"uid":160760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"美國國會跨黨派議員本月中提出修訂版本的《香港人權與民主法案》，《蘋果日報》報道，法案除促請中國政府繼續允許港人以高度自治及不受不當干預方式管治香港，同時確保香港選民可自由享有通過普選方式選舉特首及立法會全體議員的權利外，還加入了要求香港在2020年實現普選的期限。<br />\n<br />\n《香港人權與民主法案》由美國國會及行政當局中國委員會（CECC）主席兼共和黨眾議員史密斯（Chris Smith）、民主黨眾議員麥高文（James McGovern）以及共和黨參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）首先於2016年提出，翌年提交到參眾兩院，但未有過所屬委員會與國家全體投票。報道稱，本月中提出的新版本法案加入了更多要求，包括要求香港在2020年前，以公開和直接的民主方式選舉立法會全體議員，並支持香港以真正民主方式，自由及公平地提名以及選舉特首。"},{"pid":"992702b67699d930f2117571ed8f1dd1380c1b32","tid":1256856,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6k6kMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6k6kMr.png&h=71ad53d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3df1dc1c2cc8cd1162d9b8981412c9172e2b7ce","tid":1256856,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"過左先講啦"},{"pid":"fd62b737c25f1307e6ed945fa6b8c4fd4d66bc2e","tid":1256856,"uid":160760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190624/20711950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190624%2F20711950&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443tC8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=912f97c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190624%2F20711950&h=37c0e7a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190624/20711950</a>"}]}